import React from 'react'
import {BrowserRouter as Router, Route, Switch, Redirect} from 'react-router-dom'
import {Row, Col, Container } from 'react-bootstrap'
import { Dps } from '../layout/Dps';
import { Tematica } from '../layout/Tematica';

export const Internal = () => {
    return (
        <Row className="w-100">
            <Col id="main" xs={{span:10, offset: 1}} >
                <Container >
                    <Router>
                        <Switch>
                            <Route exact path="/dps" component={ Dps }/>
                            <Route exact path="/tematicas/:tematica" component={ Tematica } />
                            <Redirect to="/dps" />
                        </Switch>
                    </Router>
                </Container>
            </Col>
        </Row>
    )
}
